{
  "texts": [
    "Micro-targeted ads tailor their message to individuals' specific demographic characteristics/personality traits.",
    "There are therefore reasons to be concerned about what AI polling enables at the population level.",
    "But although AI polling enables micro-targeting, these are distinct phenomena.",
    "We could imagine a world where AI polling exists, while microtargeting is prohibited.",
    "While AI polling enables technologies that can exacerbate an uneaven distribution of power at the population level, it is not directly liable to produce such (mis)uses of power."
  ]
}